CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

February 16, 2005

[Cite as 02/16/2005 Case Announcements, 2005-Ohio-531.]

*1436MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2004-2037. State ex rel. Sherman v. Sargeant.

In Mandamus and Procedendo. On complaint of Robert Franklin Sherman. On S.Ct.Prac.R. X(5) determination, cause dismissed.

Resnick, Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor and Lanzinger, JJ., concur. Moyer, C.J., and O’Donnell, J., dissent and would grant an alternative writ.
